aS' U.S. President Donald Trump\xe2\x80\x99s meeting on Tuesday evening with a bipartisan group of senators to discuss tax reform \xe2\x80\x9cwas highly productive, and will spur constructive discussion moving forward,\xe2\x80\x9d the White House said in a statement on Wednesday. \nTrump, who is pushing his overall goals of a simpler tax code with lower rates even as a detailed plan has yet to emerge, is also scheduled to hold another bipartisan meeting later on Wednesday at the White House. \n'
